							"code" : "chat := GtL gt \n\tgtPageExplanation: 'Rules for Moldable Development for Glamorous Toolkit';\r\tgtPageExplanation: 'Instructions for creating LLM tools for Glamorous Toolkit development'.\r\t\rchat sendMarkdown:  'Create an LLM tool for returning the information about a single file. It receives as a parameter a filePath of type {{gtClass:GtLFilePathReference}} . Should return a new subclass of {{gtClass:GtLMagritteDomainObjectExamples}} containing information about the file. It should include: Size, Creation time, Modified time, Access time, Type (file/directory), Permissions. Follow the rules for creating LLM tools'.  "
